Package entity.roles

Class HDBManager

java.lang.Object
entity.roles.User
entity.roles.HDBManager
public class HDBManager extends User
Represents an HDB Manager who manages BTO projects and oversees applications. The manager can create, edit, delete projects, approve/reject applications, and handle project visibility.
